# 🛣️ Development Roadmap

The platform will evolve in three major phases.

## Phase 1 — Core AI Platform

Build the reusable AI infrastructure and the deployable foundation.

* Project Management (central entity)
* Connector Framework + File Upload
* Object Storage Abstraction
* OCR & Parsing
* Chunking
* Embeddings
* Vector Storage
* Hybrid Retrieval
* Chat
* Configuration
* Background Jobs
* Authentication
* Database Migrations
* Containerization (Docker + docker-compose)
* Evaluation Foundation
* Observability Foundation

---

## Phase 2 — Enterprise AI Platform

Expand enterprise capabilities, building concrete connectors on the Phase 1 framework.

* SQL Connector
* API Connector
* Website Connector
* SharePoint Connector
* Google Drive Connector
* S3 Connector
* Voice
* Streaming
* Multi-modal Processing
* Model Registry
* Prompt Library
* Usage Analytics
* Cost Tracking
* Evaluation Dashboard

---

## Phase 3 — Advanced AI Platform

Introduce advanced AI capabilities.

* GraphRAG
* Knowledge Graphs
* Entity Extraction
* Query Planning
* Query Rewriting
* Multi-hop Retrieval
* Memory Layer
* Agent Workflows
* MCP Integration
* Fine-tuning Experiments
* Benchmarking
* Distributed Inference
* Kubernetes Deployment

